import React from "react";
import { Form,Button } from "react-bootstrap";

export default function index() {
  return (
    <Form>
      <Form.Group>
        <Form.Control
          type="text"
          placeholder="Username"
          name="username"
          required
        />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group>
        <Form.Control
          type="password"
          placeholder="Password"
          name="password"
          required
        />
      </Form.Group>
      <Button variant="success" type="submit">
        Login
      </Button>
    </Form>
    
  );
}
